<p>If users can login, weâ€™ll also want to allow them to logout.  Implement a controller method that will log a user out when they visit it.  This will most likely involve deleting some content from the <code class="highlighter-rouge">session</code> hash.  Use the following user story to help guide your implementation:</p>

